## Strategic Priorities

**Current Focus:**
1. Partner channel development (partners teaching AI awareness courses)
2. Direct enterprise outreach to AI transformation leaders
3. Workshop delivery and iteration

**Short-term (next 60-90 days):**
- Activate partner channel (AI Lead Accelerator offering)
- Close pipeline deals
- Build repeatable outbound motion

**Long-term (next 6-12 months):**
- Scale delivery through partner network
- Develop certified facilitator program
- Establish category ownership in "human-centered AI transformation"
